-- ATP World Tour Finals to Remain in London Through 2015, ATP Says
-- B y   D a n i e l l e   R o s s i n g h
-- 2012-11-07T12:59:03Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-11-07/atp-world-tour-finals-to-remain-in-london-through-2015-atp-says.html
The season-ending Barclays ATP World
Tour Finals for the world’s top tennis players will stay in
London through 2015, the men’s tour said.  Barclays Plc (BARC)  also extended its title sponsorship of the
tournament, which has been held in the British capital since
2009, the ATP World Tour said in an emailed statement today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Danielle Rossingh in London at 
 drossingh@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
